		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">钓客进行一段爪击，造成<span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害。<br/>增幅后，强化为颃以辉翼，进行一段爪击与一段敲击，依次造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">钓客发射长程激光，持续造成<span color="#ffacff">60%,18%,<br/>6%</span><span>伤害。<br/>增幅后，强化为恒晦危光，并可发射两次，第一次造成</span><span color="#ffacff">75%,22.5%,7.5%</span><span>伤害，第二次造成</span><span color="#ffacff">90%,27%,9%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">钓客进行一段冲刺，造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。<br/>强化为衍妄之羁，冲刺距离加长，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害；非强化状态下为罕见技。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯钓客.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="170">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯钓客.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯钓客.assets/Image_16.png')" x="723" y="650">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="64" y="501" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffacff" width="193" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffacff">异界栖兽</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ff99ff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
