		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯钓客.assets/Image_22.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="66" y="1040" width="435" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深黯护盾：<span color="#ffdfbf">200%生命值</span><span>盾，击破后同时清除其他「深黯钓客」的护盾，开盾间隔约15s。<br/>黯主召唤深黯钓客(103级)：特殊的钓客，生命值</span><span color="#ffdfbf">296145</span><span>(4.86F)，攻击力</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7832</span><span>(3.0B2)，无护盾，只会发射激光。<br/>获得护盾时，抗打断0.05，重量-50%，质量翻10倍。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
